ll.org/search/?search=Winston+Churchill Winston Churchill and Zionism] Shapell Manuscript Foundation\n* [https://www.mises.org/story/1450 The Real Churchill] (critical) and a rebuttal\n* {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070912233119/http://www.winstonchurchill.org/i4a/pages/index.cfm?pageid=892&textonly=1 |date=12 September 2007 |title=A Rebuttal to 'The Real Churchill' }}\n* {{UK National Archives ID}}\n* ''[https://www.loc.gov/exhibits/churchill/interactive Churchill and the Great Republic]'' Exhibition explores Churchill's relationship with the US\n* [http://www.chu.cam.ac.uk/archives/churchill_papers/biography/churchill_chronology.php Churchill College Biography of Winston Churchill]\n* Richard Toye: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/churchill_winston_leonard_spencer/ Churchill, Winston Leonard Spencer], in: [https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/home.html/ 1914-1918-online. International Encyclopedia of the First World War].\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.history.com/news/winston-churchills-world-war-disaster/|title=Winston Churchill's World War Disaster}}\n* [http://www.shapell.org/Collection/Historical-Figures/Churchill-Winston Winston Churchill's Personal Manuscripts]\n* [https://www.nature.com/news/winston-churchill-s-essay-on-alien-life-found-1.21467 Winston Churchill's essay on Alien Life (c.1939)]\n* [https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/observations/winston-churchills-thoughts-on-evolution/ Winston Churchill's essay on Evolution (c.1939/1950s)]\n\n===Bibliographies and online collections===\n* [http://www.museumsyndicate.com/artist.php?artist=667 Online gallery of Churchill's numerous oil paintings]\n* {{Gutenberg author | id=Churchill,+Winston+(1874\u20131965) }}\n* {{FadedPage|id=Churchill, Winston S. (Spencer)|name=Winston S. (Spencer) Churchill|author=yes}}\n{{wikilivres|Winston Leonard Spencer Churchill}}\n* {{Internet Archive author |sname=Winston Churchill}}\n* {{Librivox author |id=678}}\n* {{Art UK bio}}\n\n===