''(\uc639\uae30\uc885\uae30) Ep.122 on [http://www.yes24.com/ Yes24] [[Podcast]](\ucc45\uc77d\uc544\uc6c3)-Visible Podcast\n|YouTube\n|\n|\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_pM1iY5REMM Full]\n|-\n|2020\n|[[Lee Soo-young]]'s Let's Meet at 12:00(\uc5f4\ub450\uc2dc\uc5d0 \ub9cc\ub0a9\uc2dc\ub2e4)-Visible Radio\n|CBS\uc74c\uc545FM\n|Guest\n|\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HdtXYAWI6oI #1] [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IcZMuyod1io #2]\n|-\n|2020\n|[http://www.imbc.com/broad/tv/ent/jam/ Bae Cheol-soo Jam] Ep.3, Ep.4\n|MBC\n|Guest\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellerreport.com/life/2020-02-25---%22owned-two-porsche-in-high-school%22--yang-joon-il-s-wealthy-immigration-days-.S1-C6ZMNL.html|title=\"Owned two Porsche in high school\" Yang Joon-il's wealthy immigration days {{!}} tellerreport.com|last=Anonym|website=www.tellerreport.com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-30}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|2020\n|[[Happy Together (South Korean TV series)|Happy Together]] Ep.631\n|KBS\n|Guest\n|\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ul3nCb2Z80&t=86s #1] [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ueqJmNG6R7Q #2] [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_4nGQ-DrU8 #3] [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HdtXYAWI6oI #4]\n|-\n|2020\n|[[Park Myung-soo]]'s [http://program.kbs.co.kr/2fm/radio/radioshow/pc/index.html Radio Show] <Delicate World of Profession with JIY>\n|[[KBS Cool FM|KBSCoolFM]]\n|\n|\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BhCylEonJtQ Full]\n|-\n|2020\n|[https://sebasi.co.kr/ Sebasi Talk] Ep.1152<Message from JIY to the Unfortunate People in Competition>\n|[http://www.cbs.co.kr/tv/pgm/cbs15min/ CBS TV]\n|Lecturer\n|\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SXQQogvddWU&t=68s Full]\n|-\n|2020\n|[https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJ1dCM0Uip5Jnk9bktSU5pg <nowiki>[Announcers' Bookstore(\uc544\ub098\uc6b4;\uc11c\uc810)]</nowiki>] <JIY interview with [[:ko:\uc724\ud604\uc9c4_(\uc544\ub098\uc6b4\uc11c)|Yoon Hyun-jin]]>\n|YouTube\n|\n|\n|[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TYIABWLQu68&t=10s Ep.1] [https://www.youtube.com